alert.note: Alert for Interstate 5 Corridor; Northern Ventura County Mountains; Santa Barbara County Interior Mountains (California) Issued by the National Weather Service

info.headline: Wind Advisory issued November 16 at 2:22PM PST until November 17 at 10:00PM PST by NWS Oxnard
info.description: ...WIND ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 10 AM TO 10 PM PST FRIDAY... * WHAT...South to southeast winds 20 to 30 mph with gusts up to 50 mph expected. * WHERE...Santa Barbara County Interior Mountains, Northern Ventura County Mountains and Interstate 5 Corridor. * WHEN...From 10 AM to 10 PM PST Friday. * IMPACTS...Gusty winds will blow around unsecured objects and make driving difficult, especially for high profile vehicles. Tree limbs could be blown down and a few power outages may result.
info.instruction: Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.
